19:35.159 --> 19:36.319
I think so

19:36.960 --> 19:38.280
is that Sun Jing's plan?

19:38.520 --> 19:39.119
Of.

19:39.399 --> 19:40.240
That was Sun Jing's tactic

19:40.240 --> 19:41.820
to lure the snake out of the hole.

19:41.960 --> 19:42.760
Anyone who dares

19:42.839 --> 19:44.480
acting recklessly at the moment,

19:44.920 --> 19:46.440
then that person will be caught in his trap.

20:04.799 --> 20:05.747
Ying.

20:07.559 --> 20:08.568
Young master.

20:11.839 --> 20:12.693
Taozi,

20:12.799 --> 20:14.359
I have something to talk to Ying.

20:15.920 --> 20:16.857
Of.

20:21.319 --> 20:22.240
Ying,

20:23.119 --> 20:25.480
spies deliver the news

20:25.960 --> 20:27.960
Sun Jing failed to conquer Baiyue.

20:35.359 --> 20:36.294
Ying,

20:36.520 --> 20:37.771
are you

20:38.079 --> 20:39.520
still mad at me?

20:40.480 --> 20:41.520
This time,

20:41.760 --> 20:43.040
young master cheated me too.

20:45.960 --> 20:47.240
I just feel sad.

20:47.480 --> 20:49.000
Because, Sun Jing promised to

20:49.119 --> 20:50.559
withdrew troops from Yingzhou,

20:50.590 --> 20:53.000
I just made the Barrel Boundary
as a condition of exchange.

20:55.040 --> 20:57.068
Why are you
hiding this from me?

20:57.240 --> 20:58.615
Why did you cheat on me?

21:00.200 --> 21:01.232
Ying,

21:02.559 --> 21:03.240
we both

21:03.250 --> 21:04.599
grew up together since childhood.

21:05.420 --> 21:06.520
No matter what you think,

21:07.760 --> 21:09.760
I have considered you
as my closest person.

21:10.639 --> 21:11.482
I...

21:13.820 --> 21:16.510
I never thought of hiding this
from you or deceiving you.

21:17.040 --> 21:18.000
Just you

21:18.119 --> 21:18.960
out with Li Ni,

21:19.680 --> 21:21.200
I don't want him to know.

21:24.000 --> 21:25.720
Good plan young master this time.

21:26.520 --> 21:29.000
You know as long as I gather
with the Cui Family Army,

21:29.359 --> 21:31.040
Li Ni will definitely come along,

21:31.839 --> 21:33.319
you can act too.

21:33.340 --> 21:35.610
I do think
for the good of the Cui Family Army.

21:35.799 --> 21:37.960
Now I'm
really curious too

21:38.680 --> 21:39.639
you think

21:39.760 --> 21:41.240
for whose sake?

21:41.799 --> 21:43.480
What makes you angry and upset?

21:43.720 --> 21:45.119
Is it because of Li Ni,

21:45.599 --> 21:46.879
you even forget the origin

21:47.000 --> 21:49.040
and the reason we left Yingzhou?

21:51.839 --> 21:52.680
Ying.

21:55.860 --> 21:57.280
The young master just went back to rest.

21:58.079 --> 21:59.240
It's a waste

21:59.520 --> 22:00.839
young master talks a lot.

22:37.839 --> 22:38.879
With a good count,

22:39.120 --> 22:41.060
we can use
10 thousand soldiers in hand

22:41.060 --> 22:42.270
to attack the Capital City of Xichang.

22:42.280 --> 22:44.610
You want to attack 100 thousand soldiers
with 10 thousand soldiers?

22:45.320 --> 22:47.610
Didn't Sun Jing want
to bait the snake out of the hole?

22:47.799 --> 22:49.480
We act according to his plan.

22:49.799 --> 22:50.680
He pretended to lose,

22:50.799 --> 22:52.599
I will let him really lose.

22:53.240 --> 22:54.079
Tuan Shiqi,

22:54.480 --> 22:55.860
I have something important
to talk to you about.

22:55.879 --> 22:57.012
What thing?

22:57.200 --> 22:58.168
Come here.

22:59.040 --> 23:00.639
Can't you talk in front of me?

23:01.599 --> 23:04.200
Are you arguing with Young Master Cui?

23:07.079 --> 23:07.989
Nothing.

23:09.359 --> 23:10.231
Oh yes,

23:11.079 --> 23:12.359
there's news from the capital

23:12.620 --> 23:14.680
the army that
attacked Baiyue had lost.

23:15.119 --> 23:17.639
Sun Jing blocked this news now.

23:18.799 --> 23:20.000
In that case,

23:20.119 --> 23:21.200
meaning there are not many soldiers

23:21.319 --> 23:22.639
by Sun Jing's side now?

23:23.280 --> 23:23.839
Leftenan He,

23:24.119 --> 23:24.639
should we

23:24.660 --> 23:25.879
inform the commander-in-chief immediately

23:26.240 --> 23:28.040
to go besiege Sun Jing?

23:28.960 --> 23:29.879
It's not bad yet.

23:31.240 --> 23:33.119
I think this is a bit strange.

23:33.960 --> 23:35.680
Maybe this was Sun Jing's tactic.

23:36.720 --> 23:37.680
Li Ni...

23:39.879 --> 23:40.920
That person...

23:41.320 --> 23:42.910
The person
you won't let me mention,

23:43.040 --> 23:44.280
will he be trapped?

23:45.359 --> 23:46.359
So.

23:47.159 --> 23:48.599
He is brave and conscientious.

23:49.520 --> 23:50.879
Rarely is he baited with goodness.

23:51.559 --> 23:52.760
Sun Jing pretended to lose,

23:53.119 --> 23:54.440
surely he knows about it.

23:55.200 --> 23:57.319
After all, this

23:57.760 --> 23:58.920
is an opportunity for him.

23:59.240 --> 24:00.680
He will not miss this opportunity.

24:01.520 --> 24:02.512
Yes?

24:03.000 --> 24:04.240
What will he do?

24:06.119 --> 24:07.184
He will

24:07.970 --> 24:09.399
act according to Sun Jing's tactics.

24:09.839 --> 24:10.599
You mean,

24:10.620 --> 24:12.590
Cui Li is still patrolling and
ambushing by the river?

24:12.599 --> 24:13.040
Of.

24:13.159 --> 24:14.200
We need to gather with

24:14.210 --> 24:15.710
the army sent by Commander-in-Chief Pei

24:15.720 --> 24:17.010
and set up a military camp.

24:17.520 --> 24:18.359
Mind you,

24:18.680 --> 24:20.399
menurut amalan Tentera Zhenxi,

24:20.420 --> 24:21.930
we will send some small forces

24:22.000 --> 24:23.480
to patrol to dozens of miles

24:23.490 --> 24:24.990
before choosing
a military camp area.

24:25.020 --> 24:26.480
My little team goes further,

24:26.490 --> 24:27.440
by chance we bumped into

24:27.440 --> 24:29.079
Cui Li who led the army.

24:29.440 --> 24:31.920
Apparently, he was ready for
an ambush at night.

24:32.320 --> 24:33.870
Cui Li ready to ambush?

24:33.920 --> 24:35.200
Of course he wants to

24:35.319 --> 24:36.408
attacked Young Master Cui.

24:36.559 --> 24:37.399
However,

24:38.040 --> 24:39.520
Leftenan He

24:39.639 --> 24:41.240
with Young Master Cui now.

24:41.559 --> 24:43.319
Do we want to save it?

24:43.319 --> 24:44.189
So.

24:44.319 --> 24:45.079
Very?

24:45.240 --> 24:46.064
Of.

25:04.680 --> 25:05.280
young sir,

25:05.559 --> 25:06.480
Cui Lin and others

25:06.490 --> 25:07.920
will arrive in half an hour.

25:09.960 --> 25:11.042
Deliver my instructions,

25:11.159 --> 25:12.480
everyone get ready

25:12.599 --> 25:13.520
and cheer up.

25:13.799 --> 25:15.200
After Cui Lin was killed,

25:15.639 --> 25:17.240
everyone will be rewarded.

25:17.480 --> 25:18.402
Of.

26:41.879 --> 26:42.760
Leftenan He!

27:00.760 --> 27:01.738
Sir,

27:01.920 --> 27:03.399
we didn't succeed before.

27:03.599 --> 27:04.920
We must succeed

27:05.240 --> 27:06.680
in action this time.

27:07.720 --> 27:09.799
If we can't
kill Cui Lin this time,

27:10.599 --> 27:11.960
we will lose a big support

27:11.970 --> 27:13.079
from the King of Linzi, Li Jun.

27:13.760 --> 27:15.920
After Cui Lin returns later,

27:16.119 --> 27:18.040
he and uncle
will not let me go.

27:18.920 --> 27:19.799
However,

27:21.040 --> 27:22.920
Cui Lin must die.

29:25.440 --> 29:26.040
I remember

29:26.159 --> 29:27.319
you want to shoot Lieutenant He.

29:27.480 --> 29:29.839
You have a tough mouth, but a soft heart.

30:39.119 --> 30:40.042
Young master!

30:52.760 --> 30:54.079
Ying.

30:54.240 --> 30:55.079
Young master!

31:01.319 --> 31:03.000
Young master!

31:05.480 --> 31:06.441
Young master!

31:18.200 --> 31:19.319
Young master!

31:33.480 --> 31:34.440
Let's go.

32:13.399 --> 32:16.000
Why didn't you show up
after I was killed later?

32:17.120 --> 32:18.599
You have arrived at the very beginning,

32:19.599 --> 32:21.319
but, until now you are down.

32:22.319 --> 32:23.480
You did it on purpose.

32:23.720 --> 32:24.558
Of,

32:25.399 --> 32:26.440
I did it on purpose.

32:55.159 --> 32:56.079
Didn't think so

32:56.639 --> 32:58.680
you have succeeded

32:59.879 --> 33:00.735
prince,

33:01.240 --> 33:02.399
we are indeed putting ourselves at risk

33:02.520 --> 33:04.720
to kill Cui Lin this time.

33:05.839 --> 33:06.860
However,

33:07.040 --> 33:08.720
for the success of the prince,

33:09.200 --> 33:10.319
it's worth it.

33:11.079 --> 33:12.520
You have worked hard.

33:13.440 --> 33:15.000
I will remember your service.

33:15.359 --> 33:16.559
You will earn

33:16.839 --> 33:18.319
what you deserve

33:20.599 --> 33:21.599
I reminisce

33:21.720 --> 33:22.760
good lord prince

33:22.920 --> 33:25.359
Later, I will definitely
serve the prince faithfully.

33:27.183 --> 33:30.362
(Which)

33:43.520 --> 33:47.466
(Paglima Besar Pingliang, Cui Yi)

33:47.599 --> 33:49.319
I am the commander in chief
of the Cui Family Army,

33:49.920 --> 33:51.879
Panglima Besar Pingliang, Cui Yi.

33:53.240 --> 33:54.079
You go up.

33:54.620 --> 33:56.310
If you admit defeat,
you will not be killed.

33:57.280 --> 33:59.589
The governor ordered us to attack Yingzhou,

33:59.590 --> 34:01.010
anyone who escapes will be killed,

34:01.120 --> 34:02.550
anyone who admits defeat will be killed.

34:02.799 --> 34:03.839
My whole family

34:04.000 --> 34:05.280
supervised by the village head.

34:05.520 --> 34:06.760
If I admit defeat,

34:07.079 --> 34:09.079
my whole family will be killed.

34:13.520 --> 34:14.199
Tuan,

34:14.199 --> 34:16.239
Sun Jing's army
has been half wiped out.

34:16.520 --> 34:17.880
The other half ran away.

34:18.239 --> 34:19.719
What do we say?

34:20.040 --> 34:21.159
follow them

34:21.440 --> 34:22.679
to the capital city of Xichang?

34:24.320 --> 34:25.079
Grand Commander Cui!

34:26.079 --> 34:26.960
Grand Commander Cui!

34:27.420 --> 34:28.199
Grand Commander Cui.

34:29.000 --> 34:29.759
Grand Commander Cui.

34:29.760 --> 34:30.580
On the way Young Master Cui

34:30.590 --> 34:31.840
lead the army
back to the army camp,

34:31.840 --> 34:32.589
he was ambushed

34:32.590 --> 34:33.920
and fell into the water
with serious injuries.

34:33.920 --> 34:35.110
Now his position is unknown.

34:35.279 --> 34:36.639
Where is the person by his side?

34:37.679 --> 34:38.639
Where is Lieutenant He?

34:39.050 --> 34:40.480
When Young Master Cui was ambushed,

34:40.480 --> 34:41.840
it just so happened that the Zhenxi Army
was nearby

34:41.840 --> 34:42.910
and save some people.

34:42.940 --> 34:44.400
Ketua panglima Tentera Zhenxi, Li Ni

34:44.440 --> 34:45.239
write a letter

34:45.360 --> 34:47.000
and deploy people to send to you.

34:51.000 --> 34:52.040
(Grand Commander Cui,)

34:52.120 --> 34:53.720
(when the Cui Family Army
was ambushed,)

34:53.720 --> 34:54.910
(we happen
to be nearby,)

34:55.120 --> 34:56.310
(but, unfortunately we are late)

34:56.320 --> 34:57.670
(and Young Master Cui
has fallen into the river.)

34:57.670 --> 34:59.000
(Luckily we were able to save Ying)

34:59.520 --> 35:00.759
(to calm your heart.)

35:01.220 --> 35:03.920
(Ying is fine and resting
at the Zhenxi Army camp.)

35:04.120 --> 35:06.000
(I hope you can
lead the armed forces)

35:06.000 --> 35:08.000
(and conquered Xichang Capital
with the Zhenxi Army.)

35:08.520 --> 35:10.159
Disgusting Li Ni

35:10.159 --> 35:11.520
and really arrogant.

35:12.920 --> 35:14.239
Dare he...

35:15.279 --> 35:17.440
How dare he threaten me!

35:41.880 --> 35:43.440
Ying.

36:08.759 --> 36:10.960
Lieutenant He, take medicine.

36:17.920 --> 36:20.440
It's too hot, I'll drink later.

36:23.440 --> 36:25.000
Don't be too sad.

36:25.920 --> 36:26.800
Young Master Cui...

36:27.300 --> 36:29.159
Maybe Tuan Muda Cui
has been saved by someone.

36:30.279 --> 36:31.759
Many days have passed,

36:34.679 --> 36:36.119
but, there is no news of him at all.

36:37.719 --> 36:39.840
He was afraid that bad luck had befallen him.

36:44.239 --> 36:46.040
Maybe Muda Cui
has been saved by someone,

36:46.239 --> 36:47.960
but he needs to recover from his injury

36:48.360 --> 36:50.159
and can't come back
for a while.

36:51.520 --> 36:52.759
That's it, Taozi.

36:53.420 --> 36:55.010
Don't you calm my heart again.

36:57.279 --> 36:58.960
His body is weak

36:59.480 --> 37:01.199
and suffered serious injuries.

37:03.920 --> 37:05.710
In fact, he fell
into a rushing river.

37:07.800 --> 37:08.685
Scared...

37:10.920 --> 37:12.840
I'm afraid he won't be able to come back again.

37:18.199 --> 37:20.159
He grew up with me
since childhood.

37:23.559 --> 37:25.040
In my heart,

37:28.759 --> 37:30.960
he is like

37:31.800 --> 37:33.159
my biological brother

37:34.679 --> 37:36.000
I didn't think...

37:42.000 --> 37:42.800
Didn't think so

37:42.920 --> 37:44.759
he just died.

37:46.920 --> 37:48.000
Enough already.

37:49.360 --> 37:50.279
I know

37:50.440 --> 37:51.880
You must be very sad right now.

37:52.719 --> 37:54.440
However, you are injured too,

37:54.599 --> 37:56.559
you must take medicine

37:57.040 --> 37:58.679
After you recover,

37:58.680 --> 38:01.119
we need to hurry back to Yingzhou
to meet the Commander-in-Chief Cui.

38:10.040 --> 38:11.239
Evil Li Ni!

38:11.420 --> 38:13.159
He locked us
inside the Taiqing Temple

38:13.559 --> 38:14.880
and refuse to let us go.

38:15.279 --> 38:16.360
He locked us up

38:16.480 --> 38:17.364
like this prisoner.

38:18.440 --> 38:19.480
Didn't I say,

38:20.079 --> 38:21.840
Don't mention him
in front of me again?

38:24.679 --> 38:26.559
Find me some fruit candy.

38:26.840 --> 38:27.920
When you come back later,

38:28.040 --> 38:29.279
even the medicine has become cold,

38:29.599 --> 38:30.960
I can drink quickly.

38:33.440 --> 38:34.759
Afraid of no sweets

38:34.880 --> 38:37.000
in this Taiqing Tokong.

38:37.120 --> 38:38.780
I can't
go out to buy it.

38:40.279 --> 38:41.079
What's the word?

38:41.239 --> 38:43.040
I asked them for me

38:43.199 --> 38:44.320
a little malty

38:44.759 --> 38:46.440
and make maltose for you?

38:48.119 --> 38:49.098
I'm leaving now.

39:02.620 --> 39:03.870
Why did you pour the medicine?

39:07.920 --> 39:09.960
I am the one who is guilty
of causing trouble to the Zhenxi Army.

39:09.960 --> 39:11.420
I can die faster
if I don't take medicine.

39:11.480 --> 39:13.119
Isn't this what you want?

39:14.239 --> 39:16.360
You don't have to
save me really.

39:17.360 --> 39:19.199
If Young Master Cui and I
die together,

39:19.800 --> 39:21.279
you can also let go of anger.

39:21.280 --> 39:22.670
I will definitely save you.

39:22.770 --> 39:24.470
I don't need you
to save me.

39:24.520 --> 39:25.480
No need on that day,

39:25.480 --> 39:26.790
no need at this time.

39:26.960 --> 39:29.279
Is the Zhenxi Army extremely furious

39:29.420 --> 39:31.540
and must kill me and Taozi
for revenge?

39:31.740 --> 39:33.159
So, you locked me and Taozi up

39:33.320 --> 39:34.559
in this Taiqing Tokong

39:34.560 --> 39:36.110
and order
your troops to stand guard here?

39:36.320 --> 39:37.559
Aren't you afraid of your people?

39:37.719 --> 39:39.279
will rush here to kill us?

39:40.119 --> 39:40.746
Ying,

39:40.820 --> 39:43.440
I understand that you don't know
about the Tong Border thing.

39:44.119 --> 39:45.320
You are arrogant

39:45.470 --> 39:47.110
and used to use
overt tactics.

39:47.360 --> 39:49.040
You will not use this despicable trick.

39:49.050 --> 39:51.520
After all, you wouldn't do something
that doesn't take care of the whole thing.

39:51.679 --> 39:52.719
Even if it's your fault,

39:53.279 --> 39:54.520
you will also confess.

39:55.520 --> 39:57.079
So, I have slandered you.

39:57.199 --> 39:58.599
You did not slander me.

39:59.599 --> 40:00.400
Indeed I am

40:00.720 --> 40:01.759
which causes death

40:01.920 --> 40:03.480
your troops

40:03.880 --> 40:05.279
Just kill me.

40:05.620 --> 40:07.870
Why are you pious cats
to save me?

40:08.159 --> 40:08.920
Forgive me.

40:09.599 --> 40:11.159
I shouldn't mistrust you.

40:11.320 --> 40:12.800
However, the incident
happened suddenly,

40:13.800 --> 40:15.639
many Zhenxi Army were killed,

40:16.520 --> 40:17.800
so i lost my sanity

40:19.159 --> 40:20.310
and misunderstood you.

40:26.279 --> 40:27.719
Get out. I don't want to see you.

40:54.409 --> 40:58.901
(Tokong Taiqing)

41:07.559 --> 41:08.467
Leftenan He,

41:08.599 --> 41:09.800
this is indeed a coincidence.

41:09.920 --> 41:10.960
Originally,

41:11.840 --> 41:13.360
I'm still nervous

41:13.639 --> 41:14.719
for making maltose

41:14.840 --> 41:16.279
need two days.

41:17.440 --> 41:18.320
Didn't think so

41:18.480 --> 41:20.840
there is dim sum sent from Luoyang
in the kitchen

41:21.000 --> 41:22.279
for Li Ni.

41:22.639 --> 41:23.759
I also

41:23.920 --> 41:24.840
take some

41:25.679 --> 41:26.480
I've felt it,

41:26.679 --> 41:27.360
it is not poisonous.

41:27.520 --> 41:28.639
It's quite delicious too.

41:34.239 --> 41:35.320
What happen?

41:39.159 --> 41:40.026
Nothing.

41:40.759 --> 41:42.000
I have already taken medicine.

41:43.320 --> 41:44.920
A rat came in here earlier,

41:45.679 --> 41:47.119
I took something for the measles.

41:47.559 --> 41:48.599
It doesn't touch mice,

41:48.920 --> 41:50.239
but things are scattered on the floor.

42:05.079 --> 42:06.320
Look,

42:07.199 --> 42:09.639
ketua panglima Tentera Zhenxi itu

42:10.679 --> 42:11.960
disguised as

42:12.400 --> 42:13.880
rats too.

42:14.279 --> 42:16.400
Rats bring fruit sweets here

42:16.520 --> 42:18.320
and hurt Lieutenant He's heart.

42:18.639 --> 42:20.320
My medicine is useless.

42:24.320 --> 42:25.268
Enough already,

42:25.440 --> 42:27.119
I'm going to boil the medicine for you again.

42:41.530 --> 42:42.893
Did you go to Taiqing Temple again?

42:43.480 --> 42:44.520
Any news from Yingzhou?

42:46.400 --> 42:48.719
Cui Yi is indeed cunning.

42:49.239 --> 42:50.360
Half of Sun Jing's army

42:50.480 --> 42:51.440
He has been deleted.

42:51.880 --> 42:53.920
The other half was hunted by Cui Yi,

42:54.120 --> 42:56.310
fought while retreating,
almost reached Fuzhou.

42:56.559 --> 42:57.360
What did Cui Yi say?

42:57.840 --> 43:00.000
He quickly agreed
to our terms.

43:00.559 --> 43:01.840
However, this cunning one

43:01.850 --> 43:03.400
want us to capture Cui Li alive.

43:03.679 --> 43:05.079
It feels like he wants to

43:05.239 --> 43:06.440
revenge for his son.

43:07.880 --> 43:09.079
My eldest sister can't

43:09.320 --> 43:10.480
bear heavy responsibility.

43:11.000 --> 43:12.279
Cui Li hid where he was.

43:12.720 --> 43:14.420
If nothing happens,
then Cui Li is safe.

43:14.450 --> 43:15.960
However, if anything happens,

43:16.079 --> 43:17.559
he will definitely hand over Cui Li.

43:18.679 --> 43:19.360
Of.

43:20.040 --> 43:20.599
Shiqi,

43:21.320 --> 43:22.710
several people in Tokong Taiqing

43:22.840 --> 43:24.400
not colluding with Cui Lin,

